{Speech 2}{}{Hi. My name's Savinelly. I run the caravan between New Reno and Redding. We always need reliable guards. We leave town on the 21st of every month. If you want to come with us, be here on the 21st. }
{Speech 2 Answer 5}{}{You need a guard, right?}
{Speech 2 Answer 6}{}{What do you trade in? }
{Speech 2 Answer 4}{}{Why do you wait until the 21st? }
{Speech 2 Answer Exit}{}{I don't think this is for me. Goodbye. }
