{Speech 5 Answer 6}{}{What do you trade in?}
{Speech 5 Answer Exit}{}{I think I'll be going. Goodbye.}
{Speech 6}{}{Well, mostly we pick up, uh, medical goods - yeah, that's right - in New Reno, and trade them in Redding for gold.}
