{Speech 6 Answer 3}{}{I want to ask one more thing.}
{Speech 6 Answer Exit}{}{Hmm. I see. Goodbye.}
{Speech 7}{}{I don't know how long these damn diggers will work to put together a batch of gold. We're heading out on the 21st no matter what happens. Come see me if you want the job. }
